{"tid":2036162,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李澤鉅望「港版國安法」助香港回復正常","createTime":"2020-05-26T09:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T11:09:32.000Z","uid":46356,"like":4,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c3ecfefda9863cc3bacdb0e8cd5d9fd08fc582da","tid":2036162,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:54:00.000Z","msg":"老豆做最強黃絲<br />\n其實係想幫仔仔做掩護?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2653189/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2653189%2F&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMAxR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=cbfcf050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2653189/</a><br />\n<br />\n【港版國安法】李澤鉅望「港版國安法」助香港回復正常<br />\n15:58 2020/05/26<br />\n<br />\n全國人大正在審議「港版國安法」，據外電報道，長和 （00001） 主席李澤鉅通過集團代表發送電郵表示，香港目前處於政治動盪和營商環境充滿不確定性的氛圍，希望相關草案能夠穩定香港，助社會和經濟恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n中國於上周宣布將在香港基本法附件三中列入國家安全相關法律後，隨即惹來國際關注及質疑，而相關草案將於本周四（28日）表決。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2650000/2653189/423423_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2650000%2F2653189%2F423423_1024.jpeg&h=d91975d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 李澤鉅通過集團代表發送電郵表示，希望透過相關草案助香港恢復正常。"},{"pid":"d8179d7076361a07d625e24b949739c3b50a41b7","tid":2036162,"uid":214580,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:56:02.000Z","msg":"買晒兩邊<br />\n你唔係唔知呀"},{"pid":"ec7ea84d155ac4c4a133b96452faf78793828401","tid":2036162,"uid":302917,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:57:07.000Z","msg":"佢唔係發緊成兩個星期嘅燒咩"},{"pid":"ad02351ef24b18145552b83637d5cdc4517e7160","tid":2036162,"uid":88982,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:58:53.000Z","msg":"商家巨頭既政治觸角唔係流架<br />\n兩邊都買撚哂  邊個夠佢地黎？"},{"pid":"86cad4a1635c15fa580bf3170e446e0b0fe30234","tid":2036162,"uid":88982,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ec7